===Noun===
{{en-noun|head=[[a]] [[cold]] [[day]] [[in]] [[Hell]|cold days in hell}}

# {{idiomatic|slang}} The time of occurrence of an event that will never happen.
#: ''It'll be '''a cold day in hell''' when that happens.''

